<p>In addition to the body enhancements, Larissa has also had laser facials, fillers and botox done at the Center For Aesthetic Medicine. </p>

<p>The star is set to show off her figure off again in a CamSoda performance on Monday night - just hours away - which TMZ says will have her in lingerie that includes a g-string.</p>

